        <div class="poetry">
            <p>In the stillness of night, shadows softly unfold,<br>
            A quiet refuge where stories are told.<br>
            The glow of the screen, a familiar light,<br>
            Wrapping me gently in memory's sight.</p>

            <p>The couch cradles the weight of thought,<br>
            In silence, comfort is effortlessly sought.<br>
            Echoes of voices, both distant and near,<br>
            Whisper solace only I can hear.</p>

            <p>Here, time softens and slips away,<br>
            Beneath cinematic hues that sway.<br>
            My sanctuary in the dim-lit glow,<br>
            Where mind and heart quietly flow.</p>
        </div>
